About The Creator

Hello, I am Julio Machado, the creator of this wiki.

This wiki was built as a means to store data on projects done by students in the classroom. Originally Documentation was stored on physical and digital mediums and wasn't reliable to get all that data in one place, so I coded from the ground up this wiki.
